 },
 {
  "text": "Hello Graziele. Please remember: it is okay to ask for help. If you have a question, you can ask me. If I speak fast, you can say: please speak slowly. If you do not understand, I can repeat. There is no problem. We are a team, and I am happy to help you.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a8_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi Graziele, this is Ana. A quick reminder before the meeting. Do not worry. If you need help, just ask. You can say: Can you repeat, please? or Can you speak slowly? Everyone asks questions. It is normal. You are doing great. Good luck!",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a8_listening2.mp3"
 },
